languages.text: Авель Ханейманн ненадолго пережил технособрата. Он угас в собственной келье без видимых причин, просто отказав себе в необходимости продолжения жизненных функций.
Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.
languages.original_text: Авель Ханейманн ненадолго пережил технособрата. Он угас в собственной келье без видимых причин, просто отказав себе в необходимости продолжения жизненных функций.

traits.locale_text: Abel Haneumann, who found the body of Pasqal, did not outlive his Tech-Brother for long. He withered in his cell ceasing his existence without any apparent reason. He simply denied himself the continuation of his vital functions.

languages.text: 亚伯·哈努曼没能比他的技术伙伴活得更久。他在舱室里死去，死因无从追溯，似乎他只是单纯地自主终止了生命机能。
languages.original_text: Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.

traits.locale_text: 亚伯·哈努曼没能比他的技术伙伴活得更久。他在牢房里死去，死因无从追溯，似乎他只是单纯地自主终止了生命机能。

languages.text: Abel Haneumann überlebte seinen Techkameraden nicht lange. Er verkümmerte in seiner Zelle, bis er schließlich ohne erkennbaren Grund starb, indem er seine Vitalfunktionen einfach einstellte.
languages.original_text: Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.

traits.locale_text: Abel Haneumann überlebte seinen Techkameraden nicht lange. Er verkümmerte in seiner Zelle, bis er schließlich ohne erkennbaren Grund starb. Er untersagte seinen Vitalfunktionen einfach den weiteren Betrieb.

languages.text: Abel Haneumann ne survécut pas longtemps à son technoconfrère. Il dépérit dans sa cellule et succomba sans cause apparente après avoir simplement décidé d'interrompre ses fonctions vitales.
languages.original_text: Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.

traits.locale_text: Abel Haneumann ne survécut pas longtemps à son technoconfrère. Il dépérit dans sa cellule et succomba sans cause apparente après avoir simplement pris la décision d'interrompre ses fonctions vitales.

languages.text: Abel Haneumann no sobrevivió por mucho a su tecnocamarada. Se marchitó en su celda y murió de causas aparentemente naturales, desactivando sus funciones vitales con pura fuerza de voluntad.
languages.original_text: Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.

traits.locale_text: Abel Haneumann no sobrevivió por mucho a su tecnocamarada. Se marchitó en su celda y murió de causas aparentemente naturales. Desactivó sus funciones vitales sin más.

languages.text: アベル・ヘニュマンは、技術の同志たちがこの世を去ると、ほどなくその後を追った。彼は独房の中で衰弱し、何の理由もなく、ただ自分の生命機能が停止するのを望んでいるように見えた。
languages.original_text: Abel Haneumann did not long outlive his tech-comrade. He withered away in his cell, passing seemingly without cause, simply willing his vital functions to cease.

traits.locale_text: アベル・ヘニュマンは、技術の同志たちがこの世を去ると、ほどなくその後を追った。彼は独房の中で衰弱し、何の理由もなく、ただ自分の生命機能が停止するのを望んでいるように見えた。

languages.text: Abel Haneumann, tekno yoldaşından sonra pek yaşamadı. Hücresinde giderek çöktü ve belirli bir sebebi olmadan ölüverdi. Hayati fonksiyonları, çalışmayı birdenbire durdurmuş gibiydi.

traits.locale_text: Abel Haneumann, tekno yoldaşından sonra çok uzun süre yaşamadı. Hücresinde giderek çöktü ve belirli bir neden olmadan ölüverdi. Hayati fonksiyonları, çalışmayı birdenbire durduruvermiş gibiydi.
